<p><b>What is the latest edition of ACLS provider manual?</b> The ACLS Provider Manual includes the ACLS Reference Card Set (product 20-1120; also sold separately). This product has been updated with new science from the 2020 Guidelines for CPR and ECC and replaces the previous version (15-1005).</p>
