<p><b>What is the newest edition of ACLS?</b> The 2021 ACLS guidelines have been in effect since October 2020 when the American Heart Association released the most recent guidelines changes for BLS, ACLS, and PALS. Furthermore, these guidelines will be good through 2025 when the AHA meets again to update the guidelines.</p>
