<p><b>When was the last ACLS update?</b> The AHA and European Resuscitation Council developed the most recent ACLS Guidelines in 2020 and 2021, respectively, using the comprehensive review of resuscitation literature performed by the International Liaison Committee on Resuscitation (ILCOR) [4-6].</p>
